headline.print_headline: Bombings in Iraqi Capital Kill at Least 23 People
headline.main: Bombings in Iraqi Capital Kill at Least 23 People

lead_paragraph: A wave of explosions rocked mainly Shiite neighborhoods in Baghdad shortly after sunset on Monday, killing at least 23 people and wounding dozens, officials said.
